description.en:
What is the project about?
@LFG is a BRC-20 token that will be the native token for a BRC 20 wallet and marketplace as well as an ordial wallet/market

What makes your project unique?
BRC 20 wallet made from the ground up with features that are not currently available in the marketplace

History of your project.
@LFG is a new project that launched on 5/8

What’s next for your project?
Launch of wallet/marketplace is imminent

What can your token be used for?
lots of future interaction with the LFG.cash interface
